data.description: OPEN HOUSE CANCELLED - Under contract. Welcome to your new home! This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom townhouse is ready for you to move in and make it your own. With fresh paint and new carpet throughout, this residence exudes comfort and style. As you enter, you're welcomed into a spacious living room on the entry level, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with your family. The adjacent eat-in kitchen boasts modern appliances and conveniently walks out to a fully fenced backyard patio – the ideal spot for outdoor dining, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh air.  Venture upstairs to discover three well-appointed bedrooms and two full baths. The primary bedroom features a private ensuite bath,. The upper level's thoughtful design provides both privacy and functionality.  The lower level of this townhouse is a hidden gem, featuring a finished rec-room that can serve as a versatile space for a home office, gym, or entertainment area. Additionally, the basement houses a laundry room with ample storage, ensuring your home stays organized and clutter-free.  Convenience is key with this property's prime location. Situated near shopping and restaurants, you'll have easy access to all the essentials. But the benefits don't end there – this townhouse is part of an amenity-rich community that includes a recreation facility, club house, community center, pool, tennis courts, and tot-lots. Enjoy a vibrant and active lifestyle right outside your doorstep.  Don't miss the opportunity to call this townhouse your home. Schedule a showing today and experience the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and community living. OPEN HOUSE CANCELLED - Under Contract
